<ref name=KlipFolioCSS>[[KlipFolio]] supports custom styles using CSS syntax.</ref>
<ref name=YWExecnotes>[[Yahoo! Widgets]] can interface with COM (windows) or AppleScript (Mac OS)</ref>
<ref name=DashboardC>[[Dashboard (Mac OS)|Dashboard]] uses a technology called Cocoa Plugins.This allows for Objective-C code to be used through the plugin. The plugin is written with Cocoa and is compiled.</ref>
