===Development Tools===
As widgets are largely combinations of HTML or XHTML, CSS, and Javascript in most cases, standard AJAX tools, such as [[Eclipse (software)|Eclipse ATF]], can be used for development. Specialized tools may give access to additional capabilities supplied by frameworks such as [[Dojo Toolkit|Dojo]] or [[Rico (Ajax)|Openrico]].

