'''Consolación del Sur Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in the 62nd street in [[Consolación del Sur]], [[Cuba]].<ref>[http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/385 Museo Municipal de Consolación del Sur]</ref> It was established as a museum on 14 December 1979.

The museum holds 10 sections (numismatics, sports, history, arts, documents among others). Currently, it is closed.

